tion of military technologies influences foreign policy."  aDescription based on information from publisher. 0aDrone aircraftxGovernment policyzUnited States. 0aUnited StatesxMilitary policyxPublic opinion. 0aWarxPublic opinion. 0aWarxMoral and ethical aspects. 0aDrone aircraftxMoral and ethical aspects. 0aWar and societyzUnited States. 0aUnited StatesxPublic opinion. 4aElectronic books.1 aSchulzke, Marcus,eauthor.2 aMichigan Publishing (University of Michigan)eissuing body.40zAccess to the Michigan Publishing online version:uhttps://doi.org/10.3998/mpub.9946611